  "instructions": [
    "Bring the chicken broth to a boil in a large pot",
    "Add the ramen noodles and cook for 3 minutes",
    "In a separate pan, heat the sesame oil and add the corn kernels, cooking until lightly browned",
    "Add the mother sauce and soy sauce to the corn mixture and stir to combine",
    "Add the cooked noodles to the corn mixture and stir to coat",
    "Serve the ramen hot, garnished with chopped green onions and crushed amaretti cookies",
    "Drizzle with additional sesame oil if desired",
    "Cook poultry to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F before serving."
